\# 🎬 PRD: Agentic Operating System for Film/Series Production
\#\# 📌 Product Name  
\*\*(TBD)\*\* – Working Title: \*Agentic Creator Studio\*
\---
\#\# 📖 1\. Overview
A modular, AI-assisted SaaS platform designed to guide individual creators through the complete lifecycle of a film or series project. It leverages AI to \*\*ask guided questions\*\*, extract \*\*original IP\*\* from users, and structure their ideas across pre-production to post.
\---
\#\# 🎯 2\. Goals &amp; Vision
\- Replace or assist traditional filmmaking roles using AI agents  
\- Preserve creative originality by using AI as a guide, not a generator  
\- Enable solo creators or micro-teams to independently execute high-quality productions  
\- Reduce third-party dependencies by using \*\*self-hosted open-source AI\*\*  
\- Fine-tune models over time using \*\*RLHF based on user inputs\*\*
\---
\#\# 👤 3\. Target Users
\- Indie filmmakers  
\- Scriptwriters and showrunners  
\- Creative producers  
\- Solo storytellers  
\- Small production teams
\---
\#\# 🧩 4\. Core Modules &amp; Features
