}# Design Guidelines for NarrativeOS Creative Development Environment

## Design Approach
**Reference-Based Approach**: Drawing inspiration from VS Code's clean interface and Notion's creative workspace, focusing on productivity-focused design with dark theme optimization for extended writing sessions.

## Core Design Elements

### A. Color Palette
**Dark Mode Primary** (default):
- Primary: #1E1E1E (main editor background)
- Secondary: #007ACC (VS Code blue for active elements)
- Background: #252526 (sidebar and panel backgrounds)
- Text: #CCCCCC (primary text)
- Accent: #14A085 (creative teal for highlights)
- Success: #89D185 (status indicators)

### B. Typography
- **Primary**: Inter for UI elements and interface text
- **Code**: Fira Code or Monaco for editor content
- **Hierarchy**: 14px base, 16px body, 18px headings, 12px captions

### C. Layout System
- **Spacing**: Consistent use of 8px, 16px, 24px, and 32px units
- **16px standard padding** for panels and components
- **Split-pane layout** with resizable dividers
- **Sidebar width**: 240px (collapsible to 48px icon-only)

### D. Component Library

#### Core Navigation
- **File Explorer**: Tree structure with folder/file icons, context menus
- **Tab Bar**: Closeable tabs with modified indicators, scrollable overflow
- **Activity Bar**: Vertical icon navigation (left sidebar)

#### Editor Components
- **Multi-pane Editor**: Syntax-highlighted code areas with line numbers
- **Live Preview Pane**: Clean typography for markdown/screenplay rendering
- **Status Bar**: File info, cursor position, mode indicators

#### Interface Elements
- **Panels**: Rounded corners (4px), subtle borders, proper hierarchy
- **Buttons**: Minimal styling, hover states, icon + text combinations
- **Inputs**: Dark theme forms with focus states
- **Modals**: Overlay dialogs for file operations and settings

#### Collaboration Features
- **Share Panel**: Simple URL sharing with permission controls
- **Comments**: Inline annotations with threading
- **Presence Indicators**: Subtle user avatars in active files

### E. Interaction Patterns
- **Resizable Panels**: Drag handles between panes
- **Keyboard Shortcuts**: VS Code-inspired shortcuts
- **Context Menus**: Right-click file operations
- **Drag & Drop**: File organization and tab reordering

## Specialized Features

### Creative Format Support
- **Markdown**: Live preview with custom styling
- **Screenplay**: Industry-standard formatting in preview
- **Syntax Highlighting**: Custom themes for creative formats

### Workspace Management
- **Project Structure**: Folder-based organization
- **Auto-save**: Non-intrusive background saving
- **Version History**: Simple timeline view
- **Search**: Global project search with format-aware results

## Responsive Design
- **Desktop First**: Optimized for large screens and long writing sessions
- **Tablet**: Collapsible sidebar, touch-friendly controls
- **Mobile**: Single-pane view with slide-out navigation

## Performance Considerations
- **Lazy Loading**: Load file content on demand
- **Virtual Scrolling**: Handle large files efficiently
- **Debounced Operations**: Smooth real-time collaboration
- **Minimal Animations**: Focus on productivity over effects

