**Key improvements:**
1. **Smart Layout Adjustment** - Content dynamically resizes when panels are opened/closed
2. **No Content Overlap** - Panels dock at edges without covering main content
3. **Floating Panel Design** - Panels can be minimized to icons when more screen space is needed
4. **Responsive Boundaries** - Content and panel boundaries adjust based on content requirements
