💡 How to Use These in Your Agent
   1. Upload documents: PDF, DOCX, or Markdown of key frameworks
   2. Organize them in categories inside Gemini or Perplexity Labs
   3. Prompt examples:
      * “Using the uploaded Hero’s Journey guide, can you help me map out Act 2 of my story?”
      * “Can you list common fantasy tropes from the genre guide in the KB?”
         4. Auto-reference docs when the user asks about pacing, genre, worldbuilding, etc.
