📚 Knowledge Base for StoryWriter Gemini Custom Gem
This KB supports all writing skill levels and covers core storytelling pillars: structure, characters, genre, style, dialogue, revision, and publishing. Upload these as reference documents or link to them via Google Docs, PDFs, or embedded sources.
